data.description: Tucked away in a quiet cul de sac on the 8th fairway of D'Andrea golf course in the foothills of Sparks. This home sits on a  large .19 acre lot that overlooks the valley and D'Andrea Golf Club with uninterrupted breathtaking views. D'Andrea Golf Club offers a state of the art TopTracer driving range and a 9 hole championship golf course. Centrally located with quick access to I-80 and Veterans Parkway. Nearby shopping, dining, hiking trails and more. Open entry way greets you as you enter the home leading into the great room. Perfect for entertaining and taking in the view. An abundance of natural light brightens the home throughout. Large breakfast bar. Granite counter tops. Open concept great room. Paver patio with gazebo and koi pond. Upgraded lighting throughout the backyard. Gate leading to walking trails behind home. Primary bedroom is spacious with an open feel leading into the bathroom. His and hers sinks with walk in closet.
